      <title>CDC 报告发现养老院在 COVID 疫苗接种方面落后</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/22/nx-s1-5013681/cdc-report-finds-nursing-homes-lag-behind-in-covid-vaccinations</link>
